<p><strong>Show notes for Mac Geek Gab Podcast For August 11th, 2008</strong></p>
<p>John and Dave talk about how to filter different computers &#8212; at different times &#8212; from your wireless network, a new take on syncing &#8212; and not syncing &#8212; calendars via MobileMe, and among other things discuss everyone&#8217;s favorite topic: Beachballs!</p>
<p><strong>Sponsor:</strong> <a href="http://www.barebones.com/products/yojimbo/index.shtml" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Yojimbo</a>: Your effortless, reliable information organizer for Mac OS X. It will change your life, without changing the way you work.</p>
